latestIgtvVideos.title: Beginner's Makeup Kit - Affordable Drugstore makeup for beginners
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey there my lovelies 🌸🌸 Hope you're all doing well! A lot of you keep asking me what to buy in terms of makeup and I thought it would be helpful if I made a beginner's makeup kit video! This video contains all the things you should get if you're just starting to build your make-up kit. All the products are drugstore and very affordable. Sorry for fast forwarding the clips, the video was tooooo long without it😭 Hope this helps you! Let me know if you'd like more such videoooos xo 
Products mentioned :
- Moisturizer: @neutriderm_india
- Concealer: @lagirlindia pro concealer/ @maybelline age rewind concealer
- Foundation: @maybelline fit me / @wetnwildindia photo focus foundation
- Compact: @maybelline fit me/ super fresh compact - Blush: @sivannacolors blush - Eyeliner: @lakmeindia
- Mascara: @maybelline Hyper curl mascara / @wetnwildindia renegade mascara
- Eyeshadow Palette: @makeuprevolution - Lipsticks: @maybelline creamy matte collection - Makeup Remover: @garnierindia micellar water
